    "description": "<p><strong>Cantrip Passive:</strong> You deal +1 damage against creatures that are <strong>Impaired</strong>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>You can produce 1 of the following effects:</p>\n<p><strong>Spell Attack:</strong> You can make a <strong>Spell Check </strong>against the <strong>PD</strong> of a target within range. <br><strong>Hit:</strong> The target takes 2 Poison damage.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Action Point Enhancements</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Damage: (1 AP)</strong> You deal +1 Poison damage.</li>\n<li><strong>Range: (1 AP)&nbsp;</strong>You increase the range by +5 Spaces.</li>\n<li><strong>Sicken: (1 AP) </strong>The target makes a <strong>Physical Save</strong>. <br><strong>Failure:</strong> Target becomes <strong>Impaired </strong>for 1 minute. A creature can spend&nbsp;<strong>1 AP</strong> to make a <strong>DC 10</strong> <strong>Medicine Check </strong>on itself or another&nbsp;creature within 1 Space to end the condition early.</li>\n</ul>",
